snippet.title: Making of - Mortal Kombat 3 (high quality) [MK3 Into The Outworld - Behind the Scenes]
snippet.description:
The making of Mortal Kombat 3. Behind the scenes footage and developer interviews.

 Mortal Kombat 3: Into The Outworld was a piece of promotional material used to promote Mortal Kombat 3. It was later included along with Midway Arcade Treasures that shipped with Mortal Kombat 3.
